%body
.jumbotron
  .container
    .page-header
      %h1 CHKNTNDR
      %br
      %p Expand your professional network dining at the <br> world's best establishments.
    - if current_user
      .centered
        = button_to 'Create', new_reservation_path, class: 'btn btn-hg btn-primary', method: :get

    - else
      .centered
        = button_to 'Sign up', new_user_registration_path, class: 'btn btn-hg btn-primary', method: :get

.learn-more
  .container
    .row
      .col-md-6
        %h3 Travel Savvy
        %p.justify We know networking can be tough.  Expand your professional network organically with CHKNTNDR.  We'll help you find colleagues in your industry in the cities you're already traveling to.
      .col-md-6
        %h3 Explore New Restaurants
        %p.justify CHKNTNDR picks a curated selection of top restaurants for your dining enjoyment and finds your industry colleagues interested in the same restaurants.  Never eat a meal in your hotel room alone with CHKNTNDR's help.


